title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 705 - Conan Inside the Locked R
description:
Conan and Haibara believe they're temporarily in the clear after the Bell Tree Express fiasco, and Sonoko invites Ran and co. to practice some tennis. Things quickly go sour when there is mention of a 'special coach'. Meanwhile, the relationship between four friends takes a nose dive into another locked room murder, who are the key players, how was it done, why is this 'special coach' even here? Find out in Detective Conan 705 - Conan Inside the Locked Room!

- LucarioPK Subs
